01:07:58.960 --> 01:08:06.720
we may get some success, but we'll also leave more&nbsp;
damage behind too. So I think it's a both-hand&nbsp;

01:08:06.720 --> 01:08:14.000
becoming socially active to work for social&nbsp;
clarity, social peace, and to be personally,&nbsp;

01:08:14.000 --> 01:08:22.560
inwardly clear and at peace with oneself. I did&nbsp;
this years and years of psychedelic practice and&nbsp;

